\c 5
\s Umtshokotsho wesivumelwano usala elizweni lamaFilisti
\p
\v 1 AmaFilisti asewuthatha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu awususa eEbeni-Ezeri\x + 4.1. 7.12.\x* awusa eAshidodi\x + 6.17. Josh. 11.22. 13.3.15.46,47. 2 Lan. 26.6. Neh. 13.23,24. Isa. 20.1. Jer. 25.20. Amos 1.8. 3.9. Zef. 2.4. Zek. 9.6. Seb. 8.40.\x*.
\v 2 AmaFilisti asethatha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu, awungenisa endlini kaDagoni, awubeka ngakuDagoni\x + Hlu. 16.23.\x*.
\v 3 Kwathi abeAshidodi bevuka kusisa ngovivi, khangela, uDagoni esewile ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Isa. 46.1,2,7.\x*. Basebemthatha uDagoni, bambuyisela endaweni yakhe.
\v 4 Sebevukile kusisa ekuseni kakhulu, khangela, uDagoni wayesewile ngobuso bakhe emhlabathini phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, lekhanda likaDagoni lempama zombili zezandla zakhe kwakuqunyiwe embundwini; kwasala kuye isithombo kuphela\x + Jer. 50.2. Hez. 6.4,6. Mika 1.7.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho abapristi bakaDagoni labo bonke abangena endlini kaDagoni kabanyatheli embundwini kaDagoni eAshidodi kuze kube lamuhla\x + Zef. 1.9.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kodwa isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* saba nzima phezu kwabeAshidodi\x + 5.7,11. Hlab. 32.4. Eks. 9.3. Seb. 13.11.\x*, yabachitha\x + 6.5.\x*, yabatshaya ngamathumba ophayo, iAshidodi lemingcele yayo\x + Dute. 28.27. Hlab. 78.66.\x*.
\v 7 Kwathi abantu beAshidodi sebebona ukuthi kunjalo, bathi: Umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli kawungahlali kithi, ngoba isandla sakhe sinzima phezu kwethu laphezu kukaDagoni unkulunkulu wethu.
\v 8 Ngakho bathuma babuthanisa zonke iziphathamandla zamaFilisti kibo, bathi: Sizakwenzani ngomtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Josh. 13.3.\x*? Zasezisithi: Umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli kawubhode \add uye\add* eGathi\x + 17.4.\x*. Basebewubhodisa bewusa \add khona\add* umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 9 Kwasekusithi sebewubhodise bewuthwele, isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sasimelene lomuzi\x + 7.13. 12.15. Dute. 2.15.\x* ngomonakalo omkhulu kakhulu, yatshaya abantu bomuzi, kusukela komncinyane kusiya komkhulu; kwasekuqhamuka amathumba ophayo kubo\x + 5.11.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Basebewuthumela umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu eEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*. Kwasekusithi ekufikeni komtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu eEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*, abeEkhironi bakhala besithi: Babhodise baletha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli kithi ukusibulala labantu bakithi.
\v 11 Ngakho bathuma babuthanisa zonke iziphathamandla zamaFilisti\x + Josh. 13.3.\x*, bathi: Thumani lisuse umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli ukuthi ubuyele endaweni yawo, ukuze ungasibulali labantu bakithi, ngoba kwakulomonakalo wokufa emzini wonke, lesandla sikaNkulunkulu sasinzima kakhulu khona.
\v 12 Labantu abangafanga batshaywa ngamathumba ophayo; lokukhala komuzi kwenyukela emazulwini\x + 5.6.\x*.